author: Joaquim Barbosa
title: iOS 9 jailbreak beta announced for some 32-bit devices
text:
Developer jk9357 has announced the release of an iOS 9 jailbreak, for 32-bit devices only. The name of the tool is Home Depot, and although some users have reported the tool is not working on their device yet, the news will be warmly received by those whose legacy devices have been so unloved of late. ...
